Got it! Let me upgrade the SCSS styles for both Login and Register pages with a modern, colorful, and visually appealing design using gradients, vibrant colors, and subtle animations.


---

Modern & Colorful Login Page SCSS

.login-container {
  max-width: 400px;
  margin: 80px auto;
  padding: 40px 30px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
  color: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  text-align: center;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;

    input {
      padding: 12px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      outline: none;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      color: #333;
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;

      &:focus {
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #fff;
      }
    }

    button[type='submit'] {
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #2575fc;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;

      &:hover {
        background-color: #e0e0e0;
      }
    }

    .error-message {
      color: #ffdddd;
      background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
  }

  button:not([type='submit']) {
    margin-top: 20px;
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;

    &:hover {
      color: #ffe;
    }
  }
}


